  SIMPLE_UNDERRELAXATION_FOR_MOMENTUM    0.6
  SIMPLE_UNDERRELAXATION_FOR_PRESSURE    0.4

  TIME_INTEGRATION_SCHEME  linear

  ADVECTION_SCHEME_FOR_MOMENTUM    upwind

#------------------------
# Linear solver settings
#------------------------
